{"tid":948650,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"商務部指中美計劃下月舉行更多貿易談判","createTime":"2018-12-20T08:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T17:17:18.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b20944f94ce4916bcf500544568df686c3fcaa","tid":948650,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20181220154133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20181220154133&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0f210304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20181220154133</a><br />\n<br />\n在北京, 商務部說, 中美兩國計劃下月舉行更多貿易談判.<br />\n        中美兩國昨日舉行經貿問題副部級通話, 商務部發言人說, 雙方在會談中就舉行貿易談判的安排, 交換意見, 指兩國的貿易合作潛力巨大, 達致雙贏的性質並無改變."},{"pid":"41aed160a00430c6c4196c007f005cdd91526706","tid":948650,"uid":13008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0b20944f94ce4916bcf500544568df686c3fcaa","tid":948650,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20181220154133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20181220154133&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0f210304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20181220154133</a><br />\n<br />\n在北京, 商務部說, 中美兩國計劃下月舉行更多貿易談判.<br />\n        中美兩國昨日舉行經貿問題副部級通話, 商務部發言人說, 雙方在會談中就舉行貿易談判的安排, 交換意見, 指兩國的貿易合作潛力巨大, 達致雙贏的性質並無改變."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82775c15dded1710e43e54a2041f93265e1e4ad5","tid":948650,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"每開一次會，就互數對家一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\